sentences.english: Spontanous subarachnoid hemorrhage ( SAH) mostly arises from rupture and bleeding of intracranial aneurysms.

sentences.english: Never far from her work, the mistress of the web patiently waits.

sentences.english: Simple cysts are difficult to distinguish from arachnoid cyst or epidermoid.

The web may be a combined effort of social cobweb spiders.

sentences.english: He took a breath to clear away the cobwebs of the night as the raven flapped away.

sentences.english: Conclusion The effect of microsurgery of intracranial arachnoid cysts is satisfactory.

sentences.english: Objective To explore the techniques and indications of the surgery for intracranial arachnoid cysts (IACs).

sentences.english: Spiders catch their food, usually insects, in their web.
sentences.chinese: 蜘蛛用自己的蜘蛛網進行捕食，通常是昆蟲。

sentences.english: In your mind was being detained before you remove the cobwebs confinement.
